sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Issue as New Repo Request<br/>Issue
    participant Platform as Platform Team
    participant GH as GitHub API
    participant Template as repo-template
    participant Swarm as Bootstrap Swarm
    participant Repo as New Repository
    participant Project as GitHub Project
    
    User->>Issue: Open "New Repo Request"
    Issue->>Issue: Auto-label "new-repo"
    Issue->>Project: Auto-add to board
    
    Platform->>Issue: Review request
    Platform->>Issue: Approve
    
    Platform->>GH: Create repository
    GH->>Repo: Initialize empty repo
    
    Platform->>Template: Use as template
    Template->>Repo: Copy structure
    
    Note over Repo: Files copied:<br/>- README, LICENSE, .gitignore<br/>- CODEOWNERS<br/>- .github/workflows/<br/>- .github/copilot-instructions.md<br/>- docs/ structure
    
    Platform->>Swarm: Activate Bootstrap Swarm
    
    activate Swarm
    Swarm->>Swarm: Planner: Create task list
    Swarm->>Repo: Governance: Validate compliance
    Swarm->>Repo: CI Agent: Configure workflows
    Swarm->>Repo: Docs Agent: Initialize docs
    deactivate Swarm
    
    Swarm->>Repo: Commit customizations
    
    Repo->>GH: Run policy-check workflow
    GH-->>Repo: ✅ Pass
    
    Platform->>GH: Configure secrets
    Platform->>GH: Set up branch protection
    Platform->>GH: Configure project integration
    
    Platform->>Issue: Comment with repo link
    Platform->>Issue: Close issue
    Issue->>Project: Status → Done
    
    Platform->>User: Notify repo ready
    User->>Repo: Clone and start work
